data.meta_description: Peace-of-Yours-Cafe-TPLAN-4 - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document discusses tourism planning and development for the town of Candaba in Pampanga, Philippines. Candaba was chosen as the study location due to its natural attractions and scenic spots that depict the province's beauty. The town is known for welcoming tourists and has potential for tourism development. A new tourist attraction called Peace of Yours Caf√© is proposed, which will provide coffee, sports, and picnic activities to attract both tourists and local community.
